Package: balancedSampling
Type: Package
Title: Cross-balanced sampling according to one or more qualitative variables
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Sylvain",
           family = "Loiseau",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "sylvain.loiseau@univ-paris13.fr",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5249-9550"))
Maintainer: Sylvain Loiseau <sylvain.loiseau@univ-paris13.fr>
Description: This package helps partitioning a population into several samples where each modality of one or several qualitative variables are equaly distributed; the samples can be further reordered according to a constrained randomization scheme avoiding repetition of modalities.
